StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetProspectDisposi.onTypeById]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@prospectDisposi.onId smallint AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT ProspectDisposi.onId, ProspectDisposi.onType, ProspectDisposi.onDescrip.on
FROM [usmc].[ProspectDisposi.on]
WHERE ProspectDisposi.onId = @prospectDisposi.onId
END
